        <description>Extensions to the implementation of the Money Value Object to support exchange operations between moneys in different currencies.</description>
        <summary>
            NMoneys Exchange (plural) is an extension to the NMoneys library that allows exchange operations between monetary quantities in different currencies.
			It does so by providing a framework in which such operations can take place using some default implementations and multiple extensions points.
        </summary>
